<projectDesc><p>This transcription was made by Roderic Mullen and colleagues on the International Greek New Testament Project working towards an Electronic Edition of the Gospel According to John in the Byzantine Tradition, first published in 2007.</p></projectDesc>
<editorialDecl><p>The initial transcription file was a plain text file for use with COLLATE, later converted to XML. Further information about the transcription procedures followed may be found in the electronic edition at <ptr target="http://www.iohannes.com/byzantine/"/></p>

<p>The plain text file was converted to XML by Hugh Houghton and Catherine Smith using the project's Python conversion scripts 1.0.</p>
<p>The XML specifications used are version 1.4 of the IGNTP Guidelines available at <ptr target="http://epapers.bham.ac.uk/1727/"/></p>
